:

*Kupio* je novu knjigu. (He bought a new book.)
Ona je pre *kupila* kuću. (She had bought a house before.)
Oni su *kupovali* stvari u tržnom centru. (They were buying things in the mall.)
Moraš da *kupeš* još hrane. (You have to buy more food.)
Oni su *kupili* još jednu kuću. (They bought another house.)